1. running npx @11ty/eleventy converts the .md and the .html files and builds them into _site. 
2. run npx @11ty/eleventy --serve to start up hot-reloading local web server
3. routes are automatically created based on the folders in _site
4. Editing README.md won't refresh your browser automatically, because Browsersync requires a <body> tag in your template for live-reload to work properly.